tafsir[54]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,"Haa, Miim: Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka cortewol Al Baqarah."
  41,2,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko jippornde iwri ka Allah, Yurmetee…óo, Hinnotoo…óo On."
  41,3,"Ko Deftere fensitiraande Aayeeje mun, no timmiri, nde wa…óaa janngeteende e aarabu, wonannde yim…ìe anndoo…ìe …ìen, tawde ko …ìen nafitorta maanaaji mayre, e peewal e goonga ko woni e mayre."
  41,4,"Ko nde wewliniray…ìe gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ko Allah fodi …ìe kon e mbarjaari teddundi, hul…ìiniraynde kadi, lepte Allah muusu…óe …óen. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe, …óuurnii nden; watti …ìe nanataa peewal ko woni e mayre kon, sakko …ìe ja…ìa."
  41,5,"∆Åe wi'i: ∆Åer…óe amen …óen no uddaa sokaa, …óe haqqiltaa e ko noddataa men e mun kon, noppi amen …óin kadi, no teddiri pahu, …ói nanataa …óum. Heedo hino hakkunde amen e maa, ko wowlataa kon hewtataa men. Haray wonu e golle maa; menen kadi men wona e gole amen, men jokkataa ma."
  41,6,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan satta feere'en …ìee: anndee ko mi ne…ó…óanke wano mon. Allah wahayinii e am, wonnde Rewetee…óo mon on ka goonga, ko Rewetee…óo gooto pet, woni Kanko Allah. haray √±ii…ìee e ngol laawol …óon, …óa…ì…ìiron Mo haforaneede junuubi mon. Halkaare e lepte woodanii sirkoo…ìe rewoo…ìe ko wanaa Allah …ìen, e kafidoow…ìe e Makko …ìen."
  41,7,"∆Åe jonnataa …ìen zakka jawle ma…ì…ìe …óen, hara kadi hi…ìe yeddi fii laakara, e neemaaji mun duumotoo…ói, e lepte mun muusu…óe."
  41,8,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói yamiraa…ói …óin, hino woodani …ìe njo…ìdi duumotoondi ndi ta∆¥atah, woni Aljanna."
  41,9,"An Nulaa…óo, felu sirkoo…ìe …ìen, maakanaa …ìe: ko honn…óum yeddiranton tagu…óo On leydi ndin nder bal…óe …ói…ói : - woni Alat e tenen, - wa…óanon Mo yeradii…ìe ko rewetee, hara wanaa Kanko? Awa ko On woni Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow."
  41,10,"O wa…ói pelle e dow mayri, ko ndi tabitira, hara ndi dillaali. O e…ì…ìi nguureeji yim…ìe …ìen e kulle …óen, e mayri, nder bal…óe nayi timmir…óe …óeya bal…óe …ói…ói, woni: talaata e alarba, wonannde kala faalaa…óo lamndaade fii mun."
  41,11,"Refti O faandanii tagugol kammu ngun, tawi ontuma, hingu curkini, O daalidani ngu kanngu e leydi ndin: ardiree yamiroore Am, …óoftagol, maa karhegol, hakkunde mun. ∆äi wi'idi: Men arii ko men …óoftii…ìe. Alaa ko men faalantee hoore amen, hara wanaa e yi…ói Maa, yo Joomi amen."
  41,12,"Allah timminiri tagugol kammuuli …óin, e nder bal…óe …ói…ói: woni Alkamisa e Juma; ko e …óen bal…óe …ói…ói, woni tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, timmiri bal…óe jeegoo. Ontuma Allah yamiri kammu kalal, fiyaaku maggu, immorde e yamaruyee …óoftagol Mo rewa Mo. Men cu…óiniri kammu aduna ngun, koode, Men reeni ngu e ko seytanuuji …óin wujjata he…óoo kon. Ko jantaa koo fow, ko e…ì…ìoore Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, Anndu…óo fii tagu Makko ngun."
  41,13,"Si …ìe salike gom…óinnde ko ardu…óaa e mun kon, haray wi'u …ìe, an Nulaa…óo: mi jertinirii on lepte, sugu lepte jippinoo…óe e Aadi'en yim…ìe Huudu …ìen, e Samuuda'en yim…ìe Saaalih, tuma …ìe fennunoo …ìen …ói…óo."
  41,14,"Nde Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen ardirannoo…ìe waaju wootu ngun, gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe, hi…ìe yamira wiide, wata …ìe rewu dey, si wanaa Allah tun. Heefer…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: si Joomi amen haajuno jippinnde Malaa'ikaa…ìe Nulaa…ìe e amen, O wa…óayno …óum. Awa menen on, ko men yeddu…ìe ko nula…óon fii mun kon, tawde ko on yim…ìe honoo…ìe amen."
  41,15,"Aadi'en yim…ìe Huudu …ìen kan, e hoore ko …ìe yeddi Allah kon, …ìe mawnintinii kadi ka leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, …ìe woni e too√±ugol heddii …ìe …ìen, …ìe …óaynitorii doole ma…ì…ìe …óen wi'ugol: hara ko hommbe …ìuri men doole? Hakkee ko …ìe felliti e doolnugol. Allah ruttiri ngol wiide …ìe: E …ìee yi'aali …ìe seeditii, wonnde Allah tagu…óo …ìe On no …ìuri …ìe tii…óude doole? ∆Åe woni e yeddugol Aayeeje Allah …óe Nulaa…óo ma…ì…ìe Huudu addi …óen."
  41,16,"Men wurti henndu bittinndu e ma…ì…ìe, e √±alaa…óe ma…ì…ìe kiitaade, sabu lepte …óen; fii no Men mee…óinira …ìe lepte hoynooje …óe …ìen ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara habbitii…óe …ìe …óen, …ìuri sattude wonnde hoynay…óe …ìe, kadi, …ìe he…ìoytaa ton faabo, ko da…ónda …ìe lepte …óen."
  41,17,"Samuuda'en non, yim…ìe Saalih …ìen, Men fewnirno …ìe …ìannginangol …ìe laawol goonga ngol; kono …ìe su…ìii majjere nden e dow peewal ngal. lepte jaasinooje …óen nanngiri …ìe, sabu keeferaaku e jeddi ko …ìe faggitotonoo."
  41,18,"Men dan…óni gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…ìe Mun …ìen, huliraynoo…ìe Allah …ìen, …óoftagol yamirooje Makko …óen, wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin. Men da…óndi …ìe …óen lepte yanunoo…óe e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe."
  41,19,"√ëalnde Allah moo…ìindiroyta ay…ìe Makko …ìen faade ka Yiite, hara halfinaa…ìe Yiite ngen hino √±o∆¥∆¥indira …ìe; tawa …ìe hattanaa laawagol ngen."
  41,20,"Haa si tawii …ìe hewtii ka Yiite, …ìe fu…ó…óike yeddude kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen aduna, nan…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, e gii…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, e guri …ìalli ma…ì…ìe …óin wona e seeditagol geddi e keeferaaku ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon aduna."
  41,21,"Heefer…ìe …ìen wi'ana guri ma…ì…ìe …óen: ko fii hon…óum seeditani…óon e dow amen, ko men huuwaynoo aduna? guri ma…ì…ìe …óen jaaboo: ko Allah wowlin…óo kala huunde On, woni ko wowlini men. Ko Kanko tagunoo on, ka laawol aranol, fewndo wonu…óon aduna. Ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon laakara, fii √±aaweede yo…ìee."
  41,22,"On wonaali hi…óon suu…óitoo, fewndo faggitotono…óon geddi …óin, fii wata nan…óe mon, e gii…óe mon, e guri mon seeditoyo e dow mo. Ko tawde on gom…óinaano hasboore, wanaa fii lepte maa warjeede …ìaawo maayde. Kono on sikkuno, wonnde Allah anndaa ko …óuu…ói e ko huuwayno…óon kon, …óayniti…óon."
  41,23,"Ko …óen sikke mon bon…óe, wonunoo ko sikkuno…óon Joomi mon, …óe halki on. Wa…ótinir…óon sabu …óum, jeyaa…ìe e pertu…ìe aduna e laakara …ìen."
  41,24,"Hay si …ìee …ìe tere mun seeditii e dow mun mu√±√±ike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaa∆¥ode ma…ì…ìe; hay si …ìe …óa…ì…ìirii yarluyee Allah on huncaneede lepte …óen, …ìe wonaa he…ìay…ìe …óum, wanaa fii naatugol Aljanna."
  41,25,"Men heblani …ìee heefer…ìe, seytanuuji ko …ìe wonda e ma…ì…ìe, …óin lobbinani …ìe golle ma…ì…ìe bon…óe …óen aduna, e fiyakuuji laakara, …ói …ìe yejjitinaa fii mun, ha…ói …ìe hebilangol …ói. Konngol lepte ngol jojji e ma…ì…ìe ontuma, wondude e mofte yawtunoo…ìe ado ma…ì…ìe, immorde e jinna e yim…ìe. Pellet, …ìen wonuno hayru…ìe, tawde …ìe hayrinirii ko'e-ma…ì…ìe e …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe fow, √ëalnde Darngal, naatoygol Yiite."
  41,26,"Nde heefer…ìe …ìen ronkunoo tee…óora hujja on hujja goo, …ìe wasondiri wiide: wata on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare nde Muhammadu janngata e mon, wata on jebbilano nde, ko yo on sonku tuma nde janngetee, balajo'o, on foolay mo, o acca janngugol nde nodda e mayre, …ìuttiniren e makko."
  41,27,"Ma Men mee…óiniroy yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen fennu…ìe Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen, lepte sa…ótu…óe √ëalne Darangal, Men yo…ìira ko …ìuri bonde e ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon e sirku e geddi."
  41,28,"Ko ndin njo…ìdi jantaandi, woni njoddi ay…ìe Allah yeddu…ìe Mo fenni Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen: ko Yiite ngen. Hino woodani …ìe ton galle luttugol, poomaa; njo…ìdi kon ko …ìe yeddiraynoo Aayeeje Allah …óen, …ìe salii gom…óinnde …óe, e hoore ko …ìanngunoo tii…ói hujja kon fow."
  41,29,"Yeddunoo…ìe Allah fenni Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen wi'oya: Joomi amen, hollii men majjiinoo…ìe men …ìen ka jinna e ka yim…ìe: Ibuliisaa fu…ó…óu…óo yeddugol on nodda e mun, e banii-aadama fu…ó…óu…óo rufude ∆¥ii∆¥am on, men tippa e ma…ì…ìe e nder Yiite, haa …ìe wona e …ìur…ìe joltude …ìen ka Yiite, …ìur…ìe tii…óude lepte …ìen."
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'u…ìe …ìen: Joomi amen ko Allah, wanaa go…ó…óum goo, hooti …ìe tabiti e …óum, …ìe wo…ó…óitii ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e ma…ì…ìe tuma …ìe ∆¥ettitetee, …ìe wi'ana …ìe: wata on hulu maayde e ko hikkori yeeso mayre, wata on sunano ko acci…óon aduna; wewliree Aljanna mo wonano…óon e fodeede on aduna, sabu ko gom…óinir…óon kon Allah, gollu…óon ko mo∆¥∆¥i."
  41,31,"Ko menen woni yi…ó…ìe mon …ìen ka nguurndam aduna, tawde men semmbinayno on men reena on, ko menen kadi woni yi…ó…ìe mon …ìen ka laakara: ngol giggol no heddii. Hino woodani on ka Aljanna, kala ko wonkiiji mon faaletee, immorde e dakammeeji e muuyanteeji. Hino woodani on ton kadi, kala ko faalete…óon."
  41,32,"∆äum ko maraari helaandi fii hottude mon, immorde e Joomiraawo, Haforoowo junuubi kala tuuban…óo Mo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  41,33,"Alaa …ìur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude konngol, wano on noddu…óo e fii wootin…óingol Allah, o gollitiri sari'a Makko on, o golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e weltinay…óe Joomi makko, o wi'i: min on, ko e jebbilanii…ìe yankinanii Allah …ìen, mi jeyaa? Wa'u…óo non fow, ko on …ìuri yim…ìe …ìen mo∆¥∆¥ude konngol."
  41,34,"Golle mo∆¥∆¥e …óen e …óoftaare weltinaynde Allah nden, fotataa e bone maa geddi tikkinay…ói Mo …óin. Du√±ir ko …ìuri e mo∆¥∆¥ude, on bonii…óo e maa…óa; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mun, si tawii a du√±irii bone makko on mo∆¥∆¥ere, himo wa'ita wa gi…óo sa…ótu…óo giggol."
  41,35,"Hawrataa e on jikku yettinii…óo, si wanaa mu√±√±otoo…ìe lorra e bone yim…ìe …ìen; hawrataa e mun, si wanaa jom ge…ìal manngal. Tawde ko e …óum mo∆¥∆¥ere …óuu…óunde woni."
  41,36,"Si seytaane arii sowinsinirde maa bonnugol e kala, waqtu moolor Allah, yilto…óaa e Makko. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo ko wowlataa kon, Anndu…óo fii maa…óa."
  41,37,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tindinay…ói e mawngu Makko ngun, jemma on e √±alorama on ko waylondirta kon, e naange ngen e lewru ndun. Onon …ìee yim…ìe, wata sujjan naange ngen wanaa kadi lewru ndun. Sujjanee Allah tun, tagu…óo …ói On, si wonii ko Kanko rewoton."
  41,38,"Si …ìe townitorii …óuurnagol, …ìe sujjanaali Allah tagu…óo On, haray Malaa'ika'en won…ìe ka Allah …ìen, hi…ìe subbunhinoo …ìe yetta Mo jemma e √±alorma, hara …ìe haa…ìataa rewugol Mo."
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko tindin…ói e mawngu e gootaagu e kattal Makko wuurnitugol, tawde a yi'ay leydi ndin no yoori, ndi alaa pu…ói. Si wonii non Men jippinii ndiyam to…ìo e mayri, ndi dillira aawdi mariindi e mayri ndin, ndi fontoo. Awa wuurnitu…óo ndii leydi On pu…ói, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ìe …ìen, fii √±aaweede yo…ìee, tawde pellet, ko O hattan…óo kala huunde. Wuurnitugol leydi yoorunoondi ronkintaa Mo, wanaa fii wuurnitugol maay…ìe e genaale mun."
  41,40,"Pellet, oo√±otoo…ìe …ìen e Aayeeje Amen Alla …óen, …ìe yedda …óe …ìe fenna, …ìe wayla …óe, fii ma…ì…ìe suu…óaaki Men; Me…óen anndi fii ma…ì…ìe. E ko feroytee…óo on ka Yiite …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude kaa ko aroyoowo on √ëalnde Darngal himo hoolii da…óugol lepte? Onon …ìee yiim…ìe, huuwee ko yi…óu…óon e mo∆¥∆¥ere maa bone, Men …ìannginanii on …óate mo∆¥∆¥ere e bone …óen fow. Ko pellet, Allah no reeni ko golloton e …óin kon. Hunnde e kuu…óe mon, suu…óaaki Mo."
  41,41,"Yeddunoo…ìe …ìen Alqur'aana tuma nde arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, immorde e Allah, ko leptoytee…ìe √ëalnde Darngal, feere mun alaa. Pellet non, ko nde Deftere teddunde foolunde. Gooto hattanaa waylude nden, maa wattita nde."
  41,42,"Meere iwrantaa nde yeeso mayre, wanaa …ìaawo mayre; foti koi …óuytugol maa …ìeydugol, waylugol maa wattitugol. Ko nde jipporiinde immorde ka √ëee√±o e tagu Mun, e e…ì…ìoore Mun e sari'a Mun On, Yettinii…óo e kala fiyaaku On."
  41,43,"A wi'aaka an Nulaa…óo, immorde e fenneede, si wanaa ko Nulaa…ìe adinoo…ìe ma …ìen wi'anoo. Mu√±√±o, sabu pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee kala tuuban…óo Mo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, e Jom lepte muusu…óe e kala ha…ì…ìitii…óo e junuubi, o ronki tuubude."
  41,44,"Si Men wa…óuno ndee Alqur'aanaare e haala goo, hara wanaa aarabu, heefer…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen wi'ayno: ko ha…óno Aayeeje mayre …óen …ìannginiree, no men faamira? Alqur'aana wonay e haala ajami, ardu…óo e mayre on wona aarabuujo? An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee: Alqur'aana, wonannde gom…óim…ìe Allah …ìen …ìe goongini Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen, ko fewnaynde itta e majjere, e sellinaynde √±abbuuli majjere …óin ka …ìernde e ko jokki …óum. ∆Åe gom…óim…ìe …ìen kan Allah, pahu no e noppi ma…ì…ìe …óin, kayre hinde ni…ì…ìitani …ìe, …ìe faamataa nde. ∆Åen siforii…ìe …óin sifaaji, hino wa'i wa noddirtee…ìe e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo, ko honno …ìe nanirta ndun noddaandu?"
  41,45,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Tawreetaare nden, kono luutondira e mayre: wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe gom…óini nde, wo…ó…ìe …ìen yeddi nde. Si wanaa fii fodoore Allah nden, wonnde ko √ëalnde Darngal O √±aawoyta hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen, e ko …ìe luutondiri e mun kon, O √±aawayno hakkunde luutondirnoo…ìe e fii Tawreeta …ìen; O fe√±√±ina goongu…óo on e meerenteejo on, O teddina goongu…óo On, O hoyna meereejo on. Heefer…ìe …ìen kan, pellet, hi…ìe e sikke sikkitii…óo ndee Alqur'aanaare."
  41,46,"Kala gollu…óo ko mo∆¥∆¥i, ko kanko nafitorta …óum, wanaa Allah nafitorta golle mo∆¥∆¥e hay gooto. Kala kadi huuwu…óo ko boni, lorra mun ko e makko yantata, wanaa Allah woni ko bone geddi gooto e tagu Makko ngun, lorrata. O yo…ìoyay kala e ko hanndi kon. Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, O siforaali wonnde, too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. O …óuytanoytaa…ìe mo∆¥∆¥i ma…ì…ìe, O …ìeydanoytaa…ìe kadi bon…ói."
  41,47,"Ko faade ka Allah tun, woni ko ganndal Darngal ruttetee: ko Kanko tun anndi nde ngal darotoo, wanaa go…ó…óo goo. Dim…óe yaltataa coombi mum (oom…ói mun), deyel kadi saawataa, ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal Makko. Hay huunde yawtataa Mo e …óin. √ëalnde O noddiroyta kafidaynoo…ìe Allah …ìen e sanamu, hara Himo felira …ìe …óen kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe wiide: ko honto woni …óin …ói kafidayno…óon e Am woni? Sirkoo…ìe …ìen wi'i: Tigi-tigi on, men qirrii ma wonnde hay gooto e amen alaa seeditotoo…óo …óum …óoo."
  41,48,"∆Åe majjondira e …óin sanamuuji …ói …ìe rawaynoo; …ìe yananee ontuma, wonnde laaworde lepte Allah …óen alanaa …ìe, wanaa da…óinrde."
  41,49,"Ne…ó…óanke on haa…ìataa toragol cellal, e jawdi, e …ìi…ó…óo ekn. Si bone baasal maa √±awu ekn memii mo, ko o heewu…óo fibtaade e ta∆¥agol e njurum Allah nden."
  41,50,"Si Men mee…óinirii mo cellal e ngalu e …ìuttu, …ìaawo jarrabuyee e √±awu memunoo…óo mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: ∆äum …óoo ko min woodani ! Tawde mi…óo haandi e mun. Mi fellitaa si Darngal daroto. Si …óum aru wa…óde, haray pellet, hino woodani lam ka Allah, ngalu e jawdi; wano O neeminirnoo e am aduna, tawde mi…óo hanndi e mun. Ma Men yeetitoyo yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen, geddi e keeferaaku ko …ìe huuwaynoo, ko ma Men mee…óinoy …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe muusuude."
  41,51,"Si Men neeminirii ne…ó…óanke on cellal e …ìuttu ekn, o welsindoo e jantagol Allah …óoftoo Mo, o …óuurnora …óum, toownugol balaaje makko. Si √±awu non memii mo, maa baasal ekn, o wona torotoo…óo Allah ko …óuu…ói, hara himo woyto e Makko fii on bone, no O huncirana mo …óum. Tawaa o yettataa Allah si O neeminii e makko, o mu√±√±otaako kadi e ko O jarriborta mo kon."
  41,52,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe: ""Yeetee lam, si wonii ndee Alqur'aanaaree ko ka Allah iwri, refti yeddu…óon nde fennu…óon; ko honno fiyaaku mon wa…ótinirta? Haray ko hommbo …ìuri majjude on salanii…óo goonga, fee√±irka hujja doolnu…óo?"
  41,53,"Aray ka Men holla heefer…ìe Qurayshi …ìen, maandeeji Amen …óin ka tatteeji leydi, tuma Allah ya√±√±anta juul…ìe …ìen, Men holla …ìe …ói e ma…ì…ìe tigiri, ka uddital Makka, haa …ìanngana …ìe ko sikke alaa e mu'un, wonnde ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko nde goonga, mo Allah seeditii wonnde ka ka Makko nde iwri. Ko hommbo non …ìuri mawnude Allah seedee? Si ko goonga …ìe muuynoo, …ìe yonndinorayno seedee Joomi ma…ì…ìe on."
  41,54,"Anndee sirkoo…ìe …ìen no e sikke fii hawroygol e Joomi ma…ì…ìe, √ëalnde Darngal; …ìe gom…óinaa laakaraa, ko …óum wa…ói si …ìe hebilorantaako ngal golle mo∆¥∆¥e. Anndee non, Allah no hu…ìindorii ganndal e kattal Makko ngal, kala huunde."
